<topic id="the-actions-sub-tab">
  <title>Actions Subtab</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Document type configuration dialog box<indexterm>Author tab<indexterm>Actions
              subtab</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Actions</uicontrol> subtab contains a sortable table that includes all the
        <xref keyref="glossentry_framework"><term>framework</term></xref>-specific actions. Each
      action has a unique ID, a name, a description, and a shortcut key.</p>
    <p>To open the <uicontrol>Actions</uicontrol> subtab, <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/>, go to
        <uicontrol>Document Type Association</uicontrol>, use the <xref
        href="preferences-document-type-association.dita#preferences-document-type-association"
          ><uicontrol>New</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>,
        <uicontrol>Duplicate</uicontrol>, or <uicontrol>Extend</uicontrol> button</xref>, click on
      the <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> tab, and then the <uicontrol>Actions</uicontrol> subtab.</p>
    <p>The following actions are available in this subtab:<dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Add16.png" placement="inline"/> New</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="the-action-dialog.dita#the-action-dialog"
                ><uicontrol>Action</uicontrol> dialog box</xref> that allows you to add an
            action.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_jwc_lst_tr"/>
              Duplicate</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Duplicates the currently selected action.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Wrench16.png" id="image_ltc_3ns_tr"/>
            Edit</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="the-action-dialog.dita#the-action-dialog"
                ><uicontrol>Action</uicontrol> dialog box</xref> that allows you to edit the
            existing action.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"/>
              Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the currently selected action.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
  </body>
